{"tid":608018,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「賢者箴言」一人多個喺賢者模式狀態下嘅諗法","createTime":"2018-03-27T19:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T16:08:03.000Z","uid":37245,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a85fc9071c13998c6d85326001bbcbf2744a668b","tid":608018,"uid":37245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T19:28:16.000Z","msg":"......我啱啱進入左賢者模式，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n突然諗到開個主題，集思廣益，集咁多位賢者的諗法，可能會發現新哲學/知識。<br />\n<br />\n雖然預左唔會有人認真看待。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開Post的信念係假設人類喺性高潮後的思想層面會進一步開拓，可以諗到平時諗唔到嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n呢個Post希望大家不限立場，隨心所欲表達自己喺賢者模式的想法 / 感覺。真係盡量希望各位回覆係喺賢者模式下的想法；而唔係平日嘅想法；如果唔係呢個post就失去左本來嘅意義。<br />\n<br />\n我先：其實人類成日都唔知自己真正想要乜嘢，所以先浪費好多時間喺各樣令自己沉淪嘅嘢上......比如性。"},{"pid":"79844192853b5889b8deb0fdcaf1ff7aa0afdfc3","tid":608018,"uid":37245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T19:49:39.000Z","msg":"相隔十五分鐘，我又再度進入賢者模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個留言係留低恥笑自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人類憑乜嘢可以贏到肉體帶來的渴望？<br />\n<br />\n可以茹素嗎？可以戒色嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我直覺話我知係可以，<br />\n<br />\n但我仲係嗰啲打完飛機就話以後唔打飛機嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d906a9ca20c488c425dd1c70add42ec8eebc3a45","tid":608018,"uid":5190,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T20:41:36.000Z","msg":"賢乜鳩者 聖人下話？"},{"pid":"aec62394c14c9487068fed1b68da05fdea4e03b6","tid":608018,"uid":17486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T20:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相隔十五分鐘，我又再度進入賢者模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個留言係留低恥笑自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人類憑乜嘢可以贏到肉體帶來的渴望？<br />\n<br />\n可以茹素嗎？可以戒色嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我直覺話我知係可以，<br />\n<br />\n但我仲係嗰啲打完飛機就話以後唔打飛機嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n意志力"},{"pid":"ae4020cfb2bf490be948231db5f54d1ad22e712c","tid":608018,"uid":41096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T21:21:32.000Z","msg":"每次都話要戒丁，但係仲係日日打。<br />\n係依一刻，我就知道我點解咁失敗。"},{"pid":"55bb3801bf48fafcfc5b18227772152d9bfe24f0","tid":608018,"uid":97776,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T22:50:59.000Z","msg":"其實我係咪需要愛情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n既然打飛機可以令自己對性行為失去意欲<br />\n溝女又係為扑野<br />\n咁買個飛機杯會唔會仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba13d375f22ff779fa023e30ad54cb469fdf407","tid":608018,"uid":6063,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T23:50:10.000Z","msg":"個post 好腥"},{"pid":"3b84f3a032ae69b9da8891356cf215069b5e5332","tid":608018,"uid":37245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ba13d375f22ff779fa023e30ad54cb469fdf407","tid":608018,"uid":6063,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T23:50:10.000Z","msg":"個post 好腥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有考慮過會唔會因為呢個原因冇人留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c527a6dbe9593553d601a67f928bd4534e0b36b3","tid":608018,"uid":97776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"以後唔打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44381a4119a727b13c2050874778a2a44757815","tid":608018,"uid":47500,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T07:22:42.000Z","msg":"每次打完丁淨係諗到四隻字<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/28/152121_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=